- Fixed the problem of directly exporting Gerber error when opening an online open source project
- Fixed the issue where when a project is opened in the education workspace, the editor does not automatically switch to the project area and open the project.
- The right-click menu of the component library list adds a menu to create multiple sub-libraries.
- Fixed the problem that when the searched library has sub-library, the parent library cannot automatically switch to other sub-library.
